{"id":236153,"type":2,"name":"3個夏天","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/41/7b/236153_djjHg.jpg","summary":"多情和劈腿，不容易有对错的区分；如同真爱和责任，很难划清界线。\r\n每个夏天的海边，都可能飘来一只瓶中信；\r\n就像每个人的心底，都会藏着一串爱的密语。\r\n让徬徨迷失的感情，找回自己最初的真心。\r\n\r\n每段爱情，都是一个夏天。不巧的是，梦伦同时拥有三个夏天。\r\n他在三段纠葛的爱情里劈腿，不但严重伤害了两个深爱他的女子，\r\n也因此失去了此生唯一的真爱——陈婕。\r\n伤心的陈婕悄然离去，只在琉璃瓶中封住心事，抛向大海，\r\n让爱随波漂流，从此渺无音讯。\r\n梦伦从拥有到失去、缘灭到缘起，一再错失真爱的机缘。\r\n他是否能重新找回第三个夏天，并且永远地留住它？","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>3个夏天</li><li><span>话数: </span>7</li><li><span>别名: </span>三個夏天</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Summer Rhapsody</li><li><span>其他电视台: </span>Youtube</li><li><span>原官方网站: </span>http://cw6.so-net.net.tw/kokoro/srmain.html</li><li><span>現官方网站: </span>http://www.kokoro.com.tw/</li><li><span>动画制作: </span>洛可可KOKORO幸福動畫電影館 (洛可可影音創意)</li><li><span>原作: </span>吳若權</li><li><span>导演: </span>Slime Yang</li><li><span>背景: </span>Empire Wu</li><li><span>音乐: </span>Kenjo</li>","eps":[{"id":772757,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772757","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":772758,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772758","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":772759,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772759","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":772760,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772760","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":772761,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772761","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":772762,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772762","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":772763,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/772763","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"relations":[{"i